  "title": "Technical Sales Engineer | Marine Offshore Solutions | Kaki Bukit Office",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Position: Project & Technical Sales Engineer</strong></li><li><strong>Basic Salary include Allowances: $4000 - $7000 [ Based on Experience ]</strong></li><li><strong>No monthly commission but entitled to Yearly Bonus !!</strong></li><li><strong>Working Days: Monday to Friday (9am-6pm)</strong></li><li><strong>Working Location: Kaki Bukit, Singapore</strong></li><li><u><strong>Industry: Marine & Offshore Safety Solutions Provider in Singapore</strong></u></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ol><li>Possess Marine / Mechanical / Electrical Engineering educational qualification</li><li><u><em><strong>Relevant sales experiences in Oil & Gas, Petrochemical or Marine Engineering or onboard vessel site services.</strong></em></u></li><li><u><em><strong>Knowledge of PAGA, CCTV, PABX, Fire Alarm Systems, Fire & Gas systems, Helideck lightings systems, Weather Monitoring systems, Aids to Navigation systems, Instruments, added advantage.</strong></em></u></li></ol><p><strong>Responsibilities & Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Autocad Drawings and project documentation</li><li>Project administration and scheduling</li><li><u>Technical Sales proposal and clarifications with customers</u></li><li>Project engineering and design</li><li>Hands-on product integration , troubleshooting, testing, etc. </li><li>Site Services on board vessel (local & overseas)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p></p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p></p>",
